2ndLine - Second Phone Number APK for Android


2ndLine - Second Phone Number for Android is a free mobile communication app that allows you to create a second phone number for your phone. This second line allows inbound and outbound calls like your original line without needing a dual sim card.


You can use your second line for specific calls and messages like a business line. The app enables you to send images, messages and texts as normal. Similar apps provide similar features including Snagit, Camtasia, ConnectWise Control, OPPO Clone Phone and Prezi.


Second number


Developed by TextNow, this app provides you with a second US or Canada phone number for your Android device. You can place or receive calls via Wi-Fi or your existing cellular network mobile data with anyone in Canada and the USA. All calls in these two countries are free, and you only pay for the internet connection. You can receive texts and phone calls without having the app downloaded on your phone. Only people within Canada or the USA can download this app.


Key features


The 2ndLine - Second Phone Number app has many features besides cheap phone calls. It allows for voicemails and transcripts, forwarding calls, setting caller IDs, passcodes, and a Google SmartLock account. You can set backgrounds and ringtones and create groups to receive images and texts with your signature. There is a quick reply functionality, and all messages will be available in your standard mailbox.


Phone calls and texts


2ndLine gives you a second local phone number to use for unlimited free calls to any USA or Canadian phone number. You can make cheap international calls and send unlimited free text and picture messages. There are offers sent to your account that you complete to earn free money or add money yourself to make low-cost international calls.


Big screen and quality


The 2ndLine app can be enjoyed on a big PC screen with your keyboard and mouse for ease of use. Your calls will be routed to improve quality via the elastic calling feature.


Your free second USA and Canadian number


2ndLine - Second Phone Number for Android gives you a second number and allows for free calls and messaging within the USA and Canada, and low-cost international calls. You can have a second line for business or leisure without a second sim card or any contracts.


